Usage: reset_annotated_transition [-help] {-all  | <port_or_pin_list>}

-help                  # Prints out the command usage
<port_or_pin_list>     # List of pins or ports to be annotated with the
                       # transition time that you specify using the slew_value
                       # parameter (string, optional)
-all                   # Resets all annotated transitions in the design
                       # (bool, optional)